<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.6">
<l>kañcaṅka ṟukkoṇṭu niṉmēl karuniṟac cemmayirp pēyai</l>
<l>vañcippa taṟku viṭuttā ṉeṉpatōr vārttai yumuṇṭu</l>
<l>mañcuta vaḻmaṇi māṭa matiḷtiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟā</l>
<l>yañcuvaṉ nīyaṅku niṟka vaḻakaṉē kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That raging Kaṃsa dispatched a black complexioned,</l>
<l rend="indent">red haired demoness to deceive you is all the talk.</l>
<l>You who stands in holy walled Veḷḷaṟai</l>
<l rend="indent">with jewelled mansions crawling with clouds!</l>
<l>Beauty! I am afraid when you stand there,</l>
<l rend="indent">come so that [I can] fasten a Kāppu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
